            "data" => "{"language":{"en":{"title":"Is Now A Good Time To Worry More About Financial.","description":"<p>Cryptocurrency, sometimes called crypto-currency or crypto, is any form of currency that exists digitally or virtually and uses cryptography to secure transactions. It\u2019s a peer-to-peer system that can enable anyone anywhere to send and receive payments. When you transfer cryptocurrency funds, the transactions are recorded in a public ledger. This means advanced coding is involved in storing and transmitting cryptocurrency data between wallets and to public ledgers.
